<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="fantastic-adj">fantastic <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /fæn'tæstɪk/    美 /fæn'tæstɪk/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>极好的</strong></h4>
<p>extremely good, attractive, enjoyable, etc.：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You've got the job? Fantastic!
你得到这份工作了？太好了！</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Our soccer team is fantastic.
我们的足球队很了不起。</p><footer>外研③ – 1</footer></div></div>